headline: ISRG Stock Gains on Q3 Earnings & Revenue Beat, Gross Margin Declines
summary: Intuitive Surgical's shares jump 17% after Q3 earnings and revenues beat expectations, fueled by surging da Vinci 5 placements and strong global procedure growth.
